msgid "智能图书管理系统"
msgstr "Intelligent Book Management System"

msgid "现代化的图书管理平台，为读者和管理员提供高效、便捷的图书查询、浏览和管理服务。探索知识的海洋，发现阅读的乐趣。"
msgstr "A modern book management platform providing efficient and convenient book search, browsing, and management services. Explore the ocean of knowledge and discover the joy of reading."

msgid "浏览图书"
msgstr "Browse Books"

msgid "精选图书"
msgstr "Featured Books"

msgid "合作出版社"
msgstr "Partner Publishers"

msgid "知名作者"
msgstr "Famous Authors"

msgid "为什么选择我们的图书馆"
msgstr "Why Choose Our Library"

msgid "精心策划的阅读体验，优质的服务保障，让每一次购买都物超所值，开启您的精彩阅读之旅"
msgstr "A carefully curated reading experience with quality service guarantee, making every purchase worthwhile. Start your wonderful reading journey."

msgid "精选优质图书"
msgstr "Premium Selected Books"

msgid "每本图书都经过专业团队精心挑选，涵盖文学、科技、艺术等各个领域，确保您购买的每一本书都具有极高的阅读价值和收藏意义。"
msgstr "Every book is carefully selected by our professional team, covering literature, technology, art, and more, ensuring every purchase has excellent reading value and collectible significance."

msgid "超值优惠价格"
msgstr "Great Value Prices"

msgid "直接与出版社合作，省去中间环节，为您提供市场最优价格。定期推出限时折扣、会员专享等优惠活动，让知识更加亲民。"
msgstr "Direct partnerships with publishers eliminate intermediaries, providing the best market prices. Regular limited-time discounts and member-exclusive offers make knowledge more accessible."

msgid "快速便捷配送"
msgstr "Fast & Convenient Delivery"

msgid "专业物流团队，24小时内发货，全国包邮服务。精美包装保护图书品质，让您尽快拿到心爱的图书，立即开始阅读。"
msgstr "Professional logistics team with 24-hour shipping and free nationwide delivery. Premium packaging protects book quality, getting your beloved books to you quickly."

msgid "正版品质保证"
msgstr "Authentic Quality Guarantee"

msgid "所有图书均为正版授权，印刷清晰，装帧精美。提供品质保证，支持7天无理由退换，让您购买无忧，阅读放心。"
msgstr "All books are officially authorized with clear printing and fine binding. Quality guaranteed with 7-day no-questions-asked returns for worry-free purchasing."

msgid "专业推荐服务"
msgstr "Professional Recommendations"

msgid "资深阅读顾问为您量身推荐适合的图书，根据您的兴趣偏好和阅读水平，打造个性化的阅读清单，发现更多精彩内容。"
msgstr "Senior reading consultants provide personalized book recommendations based on your interests and reading level, creating customized reading lists to discover more great content."

msgid "贴心售后服务"
msgstr "Dedicated After-Sales Service"

msgid "专业客服团队7×24小时在线服务，解答您的任何疑问。建立读者社群，分享阅读心得，让购书不仅是消费，更是加入知识社区。"
msgstr "Professional customer service team available 24/7 to answer any questions. Build reader communities, share reading experiences — buying books is not just shopping, it's joining a knowledge community."

msgid "快速搜索图书"
msgstr "Quick Book Search"

msgid "输入书名关键词，快速找到您感兴趣的图书"
msgstr "Enter keywords to quickly find books you're interested in"

msgid "输入书名进行搜索..."
msgstr "Enter book title to search..."

msgid "开始搜索"
msgstr "Start Search"

msgid "热门图书推荐"
msgstr "Popular Book Recommendations"

msgid "精选优质图书，为您推荐最受欢迎的阅读选择，开启您的知识之旅"
msgstr "Curated quality books, recommending the most popular reading choices to start your knowledge journey"

msgid "销量"
msgstr "Sales"

msgid "查看详情"
msgstr "View Details"

msgid "查看更多图书"
msgstr "View More Books"

msgid "开始探索知识的海洋"
msgstr "Start Exploring the Ocean of Knowledge"

msgid "立即浏览我们丰富的图书收藏，发现您感兴趣的内容，开启精彩的阅读之旅"
msgstr "Browse our rich book collection now, discover content you're interested in, and start an exciting reading journey"

msgid "立即开始探索"
msgstr "Start Exploring Now"

msgid "添加中..."
msgstr "Adding..."

msgid "已添加"
msgstr "Added"

